					<description><![CDATA[In macOS Catalina the podcast fetcher was moved from iTunes to a dedicated Podcasts app which is now missing some of the functionality that was available in the previous version. For example, the OPML import and export functionality is missing so I went looking for an SQLite database that Apple likes to use for this [&#8230;] <a href="https://kaspars.net/blog/apple-podcasts-subscriptions" class="read-more excerpt-read-more">Read&#160;more&#160;&#8594;</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>In macOS Catalina the podcast fetcher was moved from iTunes to a dedicated Podcasts app which is now missing some of the functionality that was available in the previous version.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="519" src="https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/opml-export-podcasts-1024x519.png" alt="OPML feed of Apple Podcasts subscriptions" class="wp-image-7386" srcset="https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/opml-export-podcasts-1024x519.png 1024w, https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/opml-export-podcasts-800x406.png 800w, https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/opml-export-podcasts.png 1089w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption>An OPML feed of podcast subscriptions.</figcaption></figure>



<span id="more-7377"></span>



<p>For example, the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OPML">OPML</a> import and export functionality is missing so I went looking for an SQLite database that Apple likes to use for this kind of storage (similar to <a href="https://github.com/matttrent/ibooks-highlights">highlight information for Books</a>).</p>



<p>I found a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Property_list">plist file</a> which lists all the podcast subscriptions under:</p>



<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>~/Library/Containers/com.apple.podcasts/Data/Documents/PodcastsDB.plist</code></pre>



<p>with the relevant parts looking like this:</p>



<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>&lt;array>
    &lt;dict>
        &lt;key>feedUrl&lt;/key>
        &lt;string>https://jasonbarnard.com/feed/podcast/&lt;/string>
        &lt;key>title&lt;/key>
        &lt;string>#SEOisAEO Digital Marketing Podcast - The most fun you'll ever have learning about digital from the experts&lt;/string>
        &lt;key>uuid&lt;/key>
        &lt;string>131C83A7-7244-4B9C-96CE-2847C84C9A06&lt;/string>
    &lt;/dict>
    &lt;dict>
        &lt;key>feedUrl&lt;/key>
        &lt;string>http://feeds.soundcloud.com/users/soundcloud:users:130477445/sounds.rss&lt;/string>
        &lt;key>storeId&lt;/key>
        &lt;string>956912399&lt;/string>
        &lt;key>title&lt;/key>
        &lt;string>1 Day Business Breakthrough - Helping Entrepreneurs Discover Their Next Big Idea Today |1DayBB&lt;/string>
